  "texts": [
    "This list includes all SEC enforcement actions that involve cryptocurrencies.",
    "For the class action cases, we collected all cases included in the Stanford Securities Class Action Clearinghouse Filings Database listed under \"Cryptocurrency Litigation\" in their \"Current Trends\" section (Stanford Law School and Cornerstone Research 2023).",
    "Again, these are securities class action cases that involve cryptocurrencies.",
    "This gave us an initial set of 34 class action cases and 43 enforcement actions.",
    "Next, we extracted the factual allegations sections of the cases' respective complaints."
